description:
YouTube is the world's 3rd most popular website, and video marketing is the hottest opportunity of the moment. Video producers are generating traffic on YouTube and monetizing it through YouTube partnerships, product promotions or by transferring the traffic to their products and domains.

But SEO on YouTube is very different from the traditional SEO. The parameters are different and that's why those who try to apply traditional SEO to videos haven't seen great success rates.

This course will teach you everything about video SEO that you need to know to get organic traffic on YouTube effectively.
title: How to rank videos on YouTube
